---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Dexter Brylle" description="Site Reliability Engineer with 13+ years of experience in observability, cloud infrastructure, and building reliable systems.">
  <section class="page-heading" aria-labelledby="about-title">
    <p class="kicker">Profile</p>
    <h1 id="about-title">About Me</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" aria-labelledby="summary-title">
    <h2 id="summary-title">Summary</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a Site Reliability Engineer and Technical Lead with over 13 years of experience
      bridging software development and enterprise-scale infrastructure. I specialize in
      Observability-as-Code and AI-driven reliability, with a proven track record of
      reducing production incidents by 95% and automating complex CI/CD pipelines.
    </p>
    <p>
      My work spans multi-cloud environments (GCP, Azure, AWS), container orchestration,
      and application security—with a foundation in microservices architecture and
      full-stack development.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" aria-labelledby="experience-title">
    <h2 id="experience-title">Experience</h2>

    <div class="experience-item">
      <h3>Site Reliability Engineer</h3>
      <p class="exp-meta">Macquarie Group • February 2025 – Present</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage enterprise-wide Dynatrace Monaco (Configuration as Code) for banking and financial systems across multi-cloud environments</li>
        <li>Designed and built ARV, an internal platform for intelligent service discovery and automated release verification using DQL and Davis AI</li>
        <li>Develop and maintain the ARV Support Agent, a multi-agent AI system built with Google Agent Development Kit for release failure analysis</li>
        <li>Design, provision, and maintain GCP ecosystem (GKE, Spanner, Pub/Sub, Vault, Vertex AI) using Terraform</li>
        <li>Act as security liaison, owning Security Assessment Documents for production releases</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="experience-item">
      <h3>Technical Lead / Senior Backend Engineer</h3>
      <p class="exp-meta">Manulife IT Delivery Center Asia • June 2021 – September 2024</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Managed Azure cloud infrastructure for the MOVE fitness app, including AKS container orchestration and Key Vault secret management</li>
        <li>Reduced production incidents by 95% through rigorous site reliability and engineering-led analysis</li>
        <li>Eliminated deployment-related downtime by transitioning to Blue-Green deployment strategies</li>
        <li>Acted as security liaison, performing SAST/DAST scanning with SonarQube, Snyk, and Burp Suite</li>
        <li>Developed and maintained New Relic monitoring dashboards, alerts, and synthetic monitors</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="experience-item">
      <h3>Expert Software Engineer</h3>
      <p class="exp-meta">Finastra • February 2019 – August 2020</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Directed architecture transformation to Kotlin Multiplatform for internal banking applications</li>
        <li>Maintained and enhanced Java, Angular, and DB2-based banking systems</li>
        <li>Architected a company-wide ride-sharing platform and a Facebook Messenger chatbot</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="experience-item">
      <h3>Lead Developer</h3>
      <p class="exp-meta">Make Technology • February 2018 – January 2019</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Architected and led development of a yoga booking and certification web app for international clients</li>
        <li>Optimized CI/CD pipelines and server environments, improving infrastructure reliability</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" aria-labelledby="skills-title">
    <h2 id="skills-title">Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Cloud & Orchestration</h4>
        <p>GCP, Azure, AWS, Kubernetes (GKE/AKS), Docker</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Observability & Monitoring</h4>
        <p>Dynatrace (Monaco, DQL, Davis AI), New Relic, Grafana, Prometheus, Datadog</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>DevOps & Automation</h4>
        <p>GitHub Actions, Terraform, Bitbucket Pipelines, Jenkins, CI/CD</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Languages & AI</h4>
        <p>TypeScript/Node.js, Python, Go, Vertex AI, Google Agent Development Kit</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Security</h4>
        <p>Snyk, SonarQube, Burp Suite, HashiCorp Vault, SAST/DAST, Threat Modeling</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Operating Systems</h4>
        <p>Linux (Ubuntu, Debian), Windows, macOS</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" aria-labelledby="education-title">
    <h2 id="education-title">Education</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Bachelor of Science in Information Systems</strong><br />
      De La Salle - College of Saint Benilde
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
    <h2 id="contact-title">Get In Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Open to opportunities in site reliability engineering, cloud infrastructure, and security architecture.
      Let's talk about how I can help build and maintain your next system.
    </p>
    <div class="link-row">
      <a href="mailto:dexterbrylle@gmail.com">Email Me</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dexterbrylle/" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/dexterbrylle" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="prose cv-section" aria-labelledby="cv-title">
    <h2 id="cv-title">Download CV</h2>
    <p>Get a complete overview of my experience, skills, and qualifications.</p>
    <a href="/dexter-matos-cv-2026.pdf" class="cv-button" download>
      <span class="cv-icon">↓</span>
      <span>Download CV (PDF)</span>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .experience-item {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .experience-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .exp-meta {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .experience-item ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .experience-item li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .skill-category h4 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .skill-category p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cv-section {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cv-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .cv-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cv-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cv-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
